# Exploratory data analysis
plot_intro(df)

plot_bar(df)

plot_correlation(df)

tmp <- df %>%
  select(-target, -X) %>%
  as.data.frame()

determinants_list <- colnames(tmp)

CIBER(data=df,
      determinants = determinants_list,
      targets = c("target"),
      orderBy = "target")
